{"tid":847870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"神級對決！陳奕迅出戰名人賽對戰李娜","createTime":"2018-10-04T13:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T12:03:58.000Z","uid":206545,"like":16,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2935c661847f5dcae9cc4a7b8fd43b939f8b6707","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:14:28.000Z","msg":"保誠香港網球公開賽2018賽會宣布傳奇球星李娜將與香港網球總會大使陳奕迅於10月9日晚上舉行的「星級名人賽」中揮拍較勁，屆時兩人會各自聯同一位香港球手以搶分賽（Tie-break game）形式進行雙打對戰，在維多利亞公園網球主場上綻放星級魅力﹗ <br />\n<br />\n今年的保誠香港網球公開賽將於10月6至14日舉行，周一（8號）為全民免費日，球迷可以免費入場，而周二（9號）則為「學生日」，學生將可免費睇波。門票現正公開發售，準決賽及決賽日已剩餘少量門票，球迷們想睇波就快啲買飛喇！"},{"pid":"67de14bfee86fbb2ab93de55d0706c894f61fd28","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181004/mobile/bkn-20181004203255654-1004_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181004%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181004203255654-1004_00882_001.html&d=2aUCrxJkkAbkNzL89I8rYQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=619f1253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181004/mobile/bkn-20181004203255654-1004_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssppveP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FssppveP.jpg&h=a66323f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfrbUGv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfrbUGv.jpg&h=77758ed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1ef3dadb68ec6361e6f8bdb15116047e5b7f983","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e97ba773e360948326608589afaccdc9cd3983","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"李娜2011年法國網球公開賽李娜連過四位前十球員奪得最後的冠軍，成為第一位奪得大滿貫冠軍的亞洲球員。2014年澳洲網球公開賽，李娜第三度晉級澳網女單決賽，並獲得最後的冠軍，成為第一位在澳網奪得女單冠軍的亞洲球員。"},{"pid":"73b700979e937f406e86eee7a65a025f78430e6b","tid":847870,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"李娜是誰？鄭潔才是真命之子"},{"pid":"dedf0e29114057f7204282515e282a08fa3b309e","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73b700979e937f406e86eee7a65a025f78430e6b","tid":847870,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"李娜是誰？鄭潔才是真命之子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f9b1fc7ca1beee0704c7690b89bf0fd69f034e","tid":847870,"uid":10576,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"我依家先知醫神打網球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452ff9e603f3d00793fb2492a32631dfcad47df1","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f9b1fc7ca1beee0704c7690b89bf0fd69f034e","tid":847870,"uid":10576,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"我依家先知醫神打網球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a13791f26a65a15499bf0b57feef50c0d484c7f","tid":847870,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"單丸打網球會不會渣d？"},{"pid":"8bd365040d9a7eccd78e30c66f6e5f79c90b9435","tid":847870,"uid":23445,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"叫陶傑打啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99a89dff2abaadcb963ebe96edbcc91a0a91437","tid":847870,"uid":206545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{